  <summary date="2023-08-07T15:42:04Z" status="Introduced in House">Ernest Peltz Accrued Veterans Benefits Act

This bill makes certain benefits that are payable to the surviving spouse of a deceased veteran payable to the veteran's children or dependent parents if the veteran does not have a surviving spouse.</summary>
